usage: terminator.py [-h] (-i | -r) [-t TIME] [-v]

Install a LaunchDaemon that forces shutdown at a defined time.

optional arguments:
  -h, --help            show this help message and exit
  -i, --install
  -r, --remove
  -t TIME, --time TIME  set desired execution time (default: 22:30)
  -v, --version         show program's version number and exit
